Discovery Bay Coastal Park (L Mombeong to Swan L), The central section of Discovery Bay Coastal Park, roughly between Lake Mombeong and Swan Lake. Coastal heathland and continuous beach. Public access to beach at Lake Mombeong and Swan Lake. This section is part of the Great South West Walk.
